snippet.textDisplay: I think this is a great routine - it’s a lot of product but she’s not wearing very much makeup at all and her real beauty shines through. And a lot of those skin care products can be duped by really good quality but affordable drugstore products, you just have to know your skin and know what ingredients to look out for. Even the tools can be duped with homemade options for the most part. I don’t think I would ever take two hours to do my make up but you could definitely do a quick version of this in about fifteen minutes - I say this with confidence because this is a lot like my routine and I can do mine in ten 😁
